    {
      "type": "text", "id": "principle", "x": 80, "y": 372, "width": 760, "height": 48,
      "text": "Progressive trust: new users see narrow delegation; calibrated users\nunlock broader autonomy. Escalation (“ask, don't guess”) is a feature,\nnot a failure mode — and the agent's blast radius is visible up front.",
      "originalText": "Progressive trust: new users see narrow delegation; calibrated users\nunlock broader autonomy. Escalation (“ask, don't guess”) is a feature,\nnot a failure mode — and the agent's blast radius is visible up front.",
